86
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:49,920
Then in the 20th century, numerical 
simulation came along, so you can do  

87
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:54,720
computer simulations to test theories.
Finally, in the late 20th century,  

88
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:58,160
