90
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:09,040
You collect large datasets and then draw 
patterns from them to deduce thoughts. 

91
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:12,160
This is a little bit different from how 
science used to work, where you make a  

92
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:17,440
few observations or have one out-of-the-blue 
