00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:41,360
the outside, it seems like AI for math is making.
You had a post recently where you pointed out  

336
00:30:41,360 --> 00:30:44,800
that over the last few months, 
AI programs have solved fifty  

337
00:30:44,800 --> 00:30:50,800
out of the eleven hundred odd Erdős problems.
I don’t know if it’s still correct, but as of  

338
00:30:50,800 --> 00:30:55,360
a month ago you said that there had been a pause 
