344
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:28,400
There was a month where that happened and 
that has stopped, not for lack of trying. 

345
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:33,920
I know of three separate attempts to get 
frontier model AIs to just attack every  

346
00:31:33,920 --> 00:31:38,800
single one of the problems simultaneously.
They pick out some minor observations,  

347
00:31:38,800 --> 00:31:43,040
or maybe they find that some problem was already 
solved in the literature, but there hasn't been  

348
00:31:43,040 --> 00:31:50,560
