People are using AI a lot currently. 

349
00:31:50,560 --> 00:31:55,600
Someone might use AI to generate a possible 
proof strategy, and then another person will  

350
00:31:55,600 --> 00:32:01,600
use a separate AI tool to critique it, rewrite 
