376
00:34:26,080 --> 00:34:29,920
The bearish one being, "Oh, they're only 
getting to a certain height of wall,  

377
00:34:29,920 --> 00:34:36,560
which is not as high as humans are reaching."
The second is that they have this powerful  

378
00:34:36,560 --> 00:34:41,840
property that once they achieve a certain 
